ir%20origin%20or%20influence%0Ato%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.langston.com%2F%22%3EPeter%20Langston%3C%2Fa%3E's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22mailto%3Apsl%40acm.org%26gt%3B%22%3E%26lt%3Bpsl%40acm.org%26gt%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20seminal%20oracle%0Aprogram%20which%20was%20written%20for%20the%20research%20V5%20Unix%20system%20at%20the%20Harvard%0AScience%20Center%20in%201975-76.%20%20As%20part%20of%20his%20%22psl%20games%22%20distribution%2C%0Athis%20original%20program%20spread%20to%20a%20number%20of%20sites%2C%20such%20as%20Murray%0AHill%20Bell%20Labs%2C%20Interactive%20Systems%20and%20Lucasfilm.%20%20Lars%20Huttar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22mailto%3Ahuttar%40occs.oberlin.edu%22%3E%26lt%3Bhuttar%40occs.oberlin.edu%26gt%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%0Aused%20a%20description%20of%20this%20program%20to%20write%20his%20oracle%20program%2C%20which%0Awas%20posted%20to%20alt.sources%20in%20August%201989.%20%20This%20program%20inspired%20the%0AUsenet%20Oracle.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fkinzler.com%2Fme%2F%22%3ESteve%20Kinzler%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22mailto%3Asteve%40kinzler.com%22%3E%26lt%3Bsteve%40kinzler.com%26gt%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%0Aa%20systems%20administrator%20and%20graduate%20student%20at%20Indiana%20University%2C%0Ainstalled%20Huttar's%20program%20on%20silver.ucs.indiana.edu%2C%20where%20it%20proved%0Ato%20be%20quite%20popular.%20%20The%20best%20Oracularities%20were%20posted%20to%20in.bizarre%2C%0Aa%20group%20local%20to%20Indiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3ERay%20Moody%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22mailto%3Amoody%40pittpa.cray.com%22%3E%26lt%3Bmoody%40pittpa.cray.com%26gt%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%0Aa%20graduate%20student%20at%20Purdue%20University%2C%20after%20correspondence%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fkinzler.com%2Fme%2F%22%3EKinzler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wrote%20the%20core%20software%20for%0AThe%20Internet%20Oracle%3Csup%3E%3Csmall%3ETM%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fsup%3E%2C%20a%20mail-based%20oracle%20program%20to%20be%0Arun%20on%20iuvax.cs.indiana.edu%20for%20net-wide%20use%2C%20where%20it%20proved%20to